What this means for the thinker architecture\
Instead of:\
\
Injecting text into \{research_findings\} (current approach)\
Running a fold over the corpus (previous discussion)\
You'd do:\
\
Spawn specialist agents with curated contexts, each carrying a specific slice of knowledge\
Introduce them to the swarm \'97 their output goes into the corpus as row_type='thought' rows\
